OASISFormat:      0.4
Name:             gsl
Version:          1.18.1
Synopsis:         GSL - Bindings to the GNU Scientific Library
Description:      GSL - Bindings to the GNU Scientific Library
  This version branched off from Olivier Andrieu's distribution
  (ocamlgsl) and includes patches as well as numerous
  API improvements.
Authors:          Olivier Andrieu <oandrieu@gmail.com>,
                  Markus Mottl <markus.mottl@gmail.com>
